{"messages":[{"role":"user","content":"Explain JavaScript vs Python"},{"role":"assistant","content":"Main differences:\n- **Syntax**: JS uses braces and semicolons; Python uses indentation\n- **Where it runs**: JS in browsers and Node.js; Python on servers, for AI, scripts\n- **Speed**: JS is usually faster (V8 engine)\n- **Use cases**: JS for web; Python for data, AI, automation"}]}
